timeline.bodyText:
I believe the port can be injected as a field using annotation @LocalServerPort, that removes the dependency of the test on configuration. Similarly to process-usertasks-with-security-oidc-springboot
   @LocalServerPort
    int randomServerPort;

    @BeforeAll
    public void before() {
        RestAssured.port = randomServerPort;
    }

